00:16:55,153 --> 00:17:00,000
♪ as gorgeous as swan, ♪

290
00:17:00,698 --> 00:17:05,552
♪ and descending blue blood. ♪

291
00:17:06,450 --> 00:17:12,078
♪ That's me, the royal princess. ♪

292
00:17:23,525 --> 00:17:25,094
If you've finished your line,

293
00:17:26,161 --> 00:17:26,974
I'll take my turn

294
00:17:27,748 --> 00:17:29,932
to sing.

295
00:17:30,082 --> 00:17:31,483
Wait. Hold on.

296
00:17:32,134 --> 00:17:33,685
You'll sing?

297
00:17:34,770 --> 00:17:35,832
Why?

298
00:17:35,832 --> 00:17:39,775
I'm confident in my voice.

299
00:17:40,125 --> 00:17:40,625
Ah.

300
00:17:40,915 --> 00:17:41,896
Look at you.

301
00:17:41,896 --> 00:17:42,949
What a confidence.

302
00:17:42,949 --> 00:17:45,771
Where did you get this kind of confidence?

303
00:17:53,839 --> 00:17:54,522
Enough.

304
00:17:55,199 --> 00:17:56,807
Stop arguing.

305
00:17:58,162 --> 00:17:59,093
Start singing.

306
00:18:13,644 --> 00:18:20,000
♪ I'm Lynchee, a lady-court. ♪

307
00:18:20,509 --> 00:18:23,767
♪ My duty is to serve her ♪

308
00:18:24,796 --> 00:18:28,731
♪ with all my heart. ♪

309
00:18:29,481 --> 00:18:35,303
♪ Looking after her everyday. ♪

310
00:18:36,244 --> 00:18:40,566
♪ Staying by her side ♪

311
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:48,175
♪ and never be apart from her. ♪

312
00:18:58,086 --> 00:19:00,722
Why don't you sing?

313
00:19:02,608 --> 00:19:03,842
My voice is a little horse lately.

314
00:19:04,326 --> 00:19:06,645
Doctor said I need to rest.

315
00:19:07,963 --> 00:19:09,347
I see~

316
00:19:32,812 --> 00:19:37,666
♪ Pretty girl, how gorgeous you are.♪

317
00:19:37,927 --> 00:19:42,878
♪ Pretty like a rose. ♪

318
00:19:43,799 --> 00:19:48,185
♪ It's like a fate ♪

319
00:19:48,559 --> 00:19:53,849
♪ that we've met. ♪

320
00:19:54,525 --> 00:19:58,730
♪ Want to stay close ♪

321
00:19:58,730 --> 00:20:00,464
♪ and look at your beauty ♪

322
00:20:00,883 --> 00:20:04,046
♪ that as gorgeous as a fairy. ♪

323
00:20:04,336 --> 00:20:08,712
♪ Do you hate me? ♪

324
00:20:08,828 --> 00:20:15,518
Why don't you talk with me?

325
00:20:23,772 --> 00:20:25,607
We're here too.

326
00:20:27,326 --> 00:20:28,445
Sorry.

327
00:20:28,832 --> 00:20:30,370
I got carried away.

328
00:20:32,214 --> 00:20:32,993
Oops.

329
00:20:33,283 --> 00:20:34,256
Who's he?

330
00:20:35,083 --> 00:20:36,139
My boyfriend.

331
00:20:37,348 --> 00:20:38,770
Excuse me.

332
00:20:40,639 --> 00:20:41,490
How do you do?

333
00:20:45,611 --> 00:20:46,383
Ploy Ying,

334
00:20:46,673 --> 00:20:48,153
I miss you so much.

335
00:20:48,443 --> 00:20:50,530
So I came here.

336
00:20:51,333 --> 00:20:53,049
If you want anything,

337
00:20:53,630 --> 00:20:55,302
just let me know anytime.

338
00:20:56,321 --> 00:20:57,285
Hmm.

339
00:20:57,575 --> 00:20:59,184
Such a sweet talker.

340
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,561
So,

341
00:21:01,561 --> 00:21:03,933
what's bring you

342
00:21:03,933 --> 00:21:05,821
to my place today?

343
00:21:07,332 --> 00:21:08,133
I want to

344
00:21:09,801 --> 00:21:11,996
hear your advice,

345
00:21:11,996 --> 00:21:12,854
Ploy Ying.

346
00:21:14,489 --> 00:21:15,974
What do you want to talk about?

347
00:21:17,042 --> 00:21:18,483
I'm here to talk about

348
00:21:19,257 --> 00:21:22,511
Tor Prakai.

349
00:21:25,968 --> 00:21:28,253
about Tor Prakai?

350
00:21:29,371 --> 00:21:30,478
Yesterday,

351
00:21:31,107 --> 00:21:32,905
I had a quarrel with him.

352
00:21:33,244 --> 00:21:34,926
I scolded him since

353
00:21:34,926 --> 00:21:37,534
he doesn't want to practice sword fighting.

354
00:21:38,695 --> 00:21:41,368
If he practiced it,
he would at least

355
00:21:41,948 --> 00:21:42,923
has some skills

356
00:21:42,923 --> 00:21:45,031
to rule Ayutthaya with me.

357
00:21:46,488 --> 00:21:47,244
But

358
00:21:47,776 --> 00:21:48,937
he interests in

359
00:21:48,937 --> 00:21:51,346
music and performing.

360
00:21:52,611 --> 00:21:53,766
Even now,

361
00:21:53,766 --> 00:21:55,809
I haven't seen his face yet.

362
00:21:55,809 --> 00:21:57,799
I've no idea how he's doing.

363
00:21:59,568 --> 00:22:00,369
Uh.

364
00:22:01,403 --> 00:22:02,204
Um.

365
00:22:03,255 --> 00:22:04,039
Uh.

366
00:22:04,122 --> 00:22:04,923
Well,...

367
00:22:05,774 --> 00:22:06,575
Gosh.

368
00:22:11,013 --> 00:22:12,280
Here.

369
00:22:21,323 --> 00:22:22,691
You should take a look at this.

370
00:22:28,530 --> 00:22:29,331
What!

371
00:22:29,931 --> 00:22:30,785
Tor Prakai

372
00:22:31,269 --> 00:22:33,098
has left the city?

373
00:22:33,485 --> 00:22:34,379
Yes.

374
00:22:34,669 --> 00:22:36,268
Your brother, Tor Prakai

375
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:37,660
secretly left this letter

376
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:38,840
at my place

377
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:39,875
since last night.

378
00:22:40,214 --> 00:22:41,990
The moment I read, I realized that

379
00:22:42,377 --> 00:22:43,818
Tor Prakai

380
00:22:43,818 --> 00:22:44,697
had already left the city.

381
00:22:45,326 --> 00:22:46,559
However,

382
00:22:47,624 --> 00:22:49,617
I have no courage to tell you.

383
00:22:50,685 --> 00:22:51,355
So I just

384
00:22:52,226 --> 00:22:53,854
kept the letter with me.

385
00:22:55,374 --> 00:22:56,174
It's okay.

386
00:22:56,975 --> 00:22:57,801
At least,

387
00:22:57,801 --> 00:22:59,152
I've known

388
00:22:59,442 --> 00:23:00,640
where Tor Prakai

389
00:23:01,269 --> 00:23:03,054
is heading to.

390
00:23:03,448 --> 00:23:05,343
Uh, where is your brother

391
00:23:05,343 --> 00:23:06,802
heading to?

392
00:23:07,135 --> 00:23:08,189
The letter

393
00:23:08,189 --> 00:23:09,676
told that Tor Prakai

394
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:12,131
is heading to Thonburi.

395
00:23:12,974 --> 00:23:14,152
I heard that

396
00:23:14,152 --> 00:23:15,197
Thonburi

397
00:23:15,197 --> 00:23:17,072
is well known for art and music.

398
00:23:17,072 --> 00:23:18,999
Artists from many fields

399
00:23:18,999 --> 00:23:20,615
