400
00:23:21,850 --> 00:23:23,652
It's no surprise.

401
00:23:24,369 --> 00:23:26,371
Your brother is following his dream.

402
00:23:28,924 --> 00:23:29,656
So,

403
00:23:29,656 --> 00:23:31,409
what should we do now?

404
00:23:31,927 --> 00:23:33,044
Yeah.

405
00:23:35,163 --> 00:23:36,414
Path to Thonburi

406
00:23:36,656 --> 00:23:38,994
is really dangerous.

407
00:23:38,994 --> 00:23:40,334
There's a lot of thieves.

408
00:23:40,334 --> 00:23:41,926
If anything happened,

409
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:44,475
he might couldn't survive back.

410
00:23:45,373 --> 00:23:46,024
Then,

411
00:23:46,798 --> 00:23:48,118
we must immediately follow him.

412
00:23:48,505 --> 00:23:49,166
Great idea.

413
00:23:49,166 --> 00:23:50,694
If we depart now,

414
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:53,173
I think we'll catch up with him.

415
00:23:53,173 --> 00:23:54,347
Everyone

416
00:23:55,073 --> 00:23:56,385
be prepared.

417
00:23:56,385 --> 00:23:58,315
We'll head toward

418
00:23:58,315 --> 00:23:59,623
Thonburi.

419
00:23:59,623 --> 00:24:01,868
To find Tor Prakai.

420
00:24:04,609 --> 00:24:05,560
After you.

421
00:24:44,579 --> 00:24:47,256
♪ Leaving from ♪

422
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:51,299
♪ my hometown ♪

423
00:24:54,347 --> 00:24:59,758
♪ due to the quarrel with my brother. ♪

424
00:25:01,725 --> 00:25:08,418
♪ I've left Ayutthaya ♪

425
00:25:10,001 --> 00:25:15,339
♪ and came to this city. ♪

426
00:25:17,465 --> 00:25:22,755
♪ Because I'm passionate in music, ♪

427
00:25:24,228 --> 00:25:30,727
♪ not combat skills. ♪

428
00:25:37,485 --> 00:25:38,881
I'm Tor Prakai,

429
00:25:39,752 --> 00:25:42,131
Prince of Ayutthaya.

430
00:25:47,812 --> 00:25:48,610
Yesterday,

431
00:25:49,045 --> 00:25:50,659
I quarreled with my brother.

432
00:25:51,433 --> 00:25:52,404
Because

433
00:25:53,275 --> 00:25:54,180
he forced me

434
00:25:54,519 --> 00:25:56,505
to practice sword fighting

435
00:25:56,505 --> 00:25:58,207
and combat skills.

436
00:25:58,207 --> 00:25:59,629
But I

437
00:25:59,629 --> 00:26:00,764
didn't want to.

438
00:26:01,248 --> 00:26:04,144
I'm passionate in music and performing.

439
00:26:05,789 --> 00:26:06,765
So I decided

440
00:26:09,050 --> 00:26:10,402
to leave Ayutthaya

441
00:26:10,969 --> 00:26:12,454
and head towards Thonburi.

442
00:26:13,405 --> 00:26:14,205
Huh.

443
00:26:16,408 --> 00:26:17,759
I've left for a while.

444
00:26:18,526 --> 00:26:20,962
I'm starving.

445
00:26:21,212 --> 00:26:22,731
And my throat is parched.

446
00:26:38,399 --> 00:26:43,060
♪ I've met a guy taking rest ♪

447
00:26:44,894 --> 00:26:50,000
♪ who is cute and fine. ♪

448
00:26:51,556 --> 00:26:56,991
♪ I want to get close ♪

449
00:26:59,134 --> 00:27:04,433
♪ and look at his face. ♪

450
00:27:05,255 --> 00:27:10,351
♪ So I grab a bottle of water ♪

451
00:27:12,931 --> 00:27:18,411
♪ and talk to him generously. ♪

452
00:27:26,961 --> 00:27:27,762
Hey.

453
00:27:30,615 --> 00:27:31,733
Are you okay?

454
00:27:32,050 --> 00:27:33,485
You look tired.

455
00:27:34,052 --> 00:27:34,853
Who are you?

456
00:27:35,770 --> 00:27:36,721
What are you doing here?

457
00:27:37,639 --> 00:27:38,973
You're not a thief, are you?

458
00:27:43,445 --> 00:27:45,363
If I'm an actual theif,

459
00:27:46,081 --> 00:27:48,333
I won't kindly talk to you like this.

460
00:27:49,284 --> 00:27:50,168
I might

461
00:27:51,519 --> 00:27:53,288
