462
00:27:58,560 --> 00:27:59,411
Then who are you?

463
00:28:00,095 --> 00:28:01,079
What are you doing here?

464
00:28:03,565 --> 00:28:04,366
Uh.

465
00:28:04,566 --> 00:28:06,534
I live in Thonburi.

466
00:28:07,252 --> 00:28:07,902
And

467
00:28:07,902 --> 00:28:10,055
I'm here to find some food.

468
00:28:10,805 --> 00:28:11,606
What about you?

469
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:13,975
What are you doing here alone?

470
00:28:16,244 --> 00:28:17,879
And you even look pale.

471
00:28:23,735 --> 00:28:26,428
Drink some water so you'll feel better.

472
00:28:27,589 --> 00:28:28,795
Water!

473
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,928
Thanks.

474
00:28:42,253 --> 00:28:43,371
Thank you so much.

475
00:28:44,773 --> 00:28:45,411
Well,

476
00:28:45,798 --> 00:28:47,883
you live in Thonburi, right?

477
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:49,571
I want to go there.

478
00:28:49,571 --> 00:28:51,260
Is it a long way to go?

479
00:28:53,081 --> 00:28:53,742
Hey.

480
00:28:54,177 --> 00:28:55,572
Don't get me wrong but

481
00:28:56,878 --> 00:28:58,328
what makes you want to go there?

482
00:28:59,521 --> 00:29:00,688
I heard that

483
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:03,204
Thonburi

484
00:29:03,494 --> 00:29:06,286
has a lot of masters in art and music.

485
00:29:07,737 --> 00:29:09,823
I want to go there and learn about it.

486
00:29:10,452 --> 00:29:12,098
To follow my dream.

487
00:29:15,370 --> 00:29:17,598
If it's really your dream,

488
00:29:19,049 --> 00:29:20,374
I'll take you there.

489
00:29:20,713 --> 00:29:21,213
What?

490
00:29:21,503 --> 00:29:22,479
Really?

491
00:29:22,914 --> 00:29:24,439
You'll take me there?

492
00:29:24,729 --> 00:29:25,613
Yeah.

493
00:29:25,847 --> 00:29:26,347
Hey.

494
00:29:26,347 --> 00:29:27,165
Thank you so much.

495
00:29:30,001 --> 00:29:31,286
My pleasure.

496
00:29:34,005 --> 00:29:34,582
Sorry.

497
00:29:35,549 --> 00:29:36,629
I'm just overjoyed.

498
00:29:40,728 --> 00:29:42,576
Well,

499
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,385
what's your name?

500
00:29:45,304 --> 00:29:47,513
I haven't known your name yet.

501
00:29:48,771 --> 00:29:50,465
I'm Pra Nine.

502
00:29:51,142 --> 00:29:52,767
What's yours?

503
00:29:53,808 --> 00:29:55,093
I'm Tor Prakai.

504
00:29:57,679 --> 00:29:59,681
So, we've known each other now.

505
00:30:03,852 --> 00:30:05,770
Then let's set off.

506
00:30:06,054 --> 00:30:08,006
It'll be dangerous at night.

507
00:30:10,291 --> 00:30:11,092
Follow me.

508
00:30:20,168 --> 00:30:21,085
Stop!

509
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:26,891
I said stop!

510
00:30:27,408 --> 00:30:28,209
We stopped.

511
00:30:29,644 --> 00:30:30,208
Wait.

512
00:30:30,450 --> 00:30:31,730
He told them.

513
00:30:31,730 --> 00:30:33,490
Not you.

514
00:30:36,935 --> 00:30:39,087
Who are you and where are you going?

515
00:30:40,171 --> 00:30:42,738
We're heading back to the city.

516
00:30:42,738 --> 00:30:43,953
I and my brother

517
00:30:43,953 --> 00:30:45,443
came here finding food.

518
00:30:46,561 --> 00:30:47,729
Any money with you?

519
00:30:47,729 --> 00:30:49,047
Send your money to me!

520
00:30:50,048 --> 00:30:50,848
Uh.

521
00:30:51,482 --> 00:30:51,982
We….

522
00:30:51,982 --> 00:30:53,685
we're just villagers.

523
00:30:53,935 --> 00:30:54,534
Hmm.

524
00:30:54,534 --> 00:30:55,781
We have no money for you.

525
00:30:55,781 --> 00:30:56,287
Hey.

526
00:30:56,921 --> 00:30:58,640
Did you mock me?

527
00:30:58,840 --> 00:30:59,691
Exactly.

528
00:30:59,924 --> 00:31:00,608
He mocked you.

529
00:31:00,608 --> 00:31:01,492
He imitated your voice.

530
00:31:01,693 --> 00:31:02,493
You're lying.

531
00:31:03,044 --> 00:31:03,845
I know you have it.

532
00:31:04,045 --> 00:31:04,846
Any money?

533
00:31:05,213 --> 00:31:06,014
No.

534
00:31:07,482 --> 00:31:08,650
You're hilarious.

535
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,051
If you have no money,

536
00:31:10,802 --> 00:31:13,121
we'll take

537
00:31:13,404 --> 00:31:14,522
your bodies instead.

538
00:31:15,006 --> 00:31:15,807
Our bodies!

539
00:31:16,174 --> 00:31:16,975
Understood?

540
00:31:17,098 --> 00:31:18,359
Yeah.

541
00:31:18,359 --> 00:31:19,085
Do you test me?

542
00:31:19,085 --> 00:31:20,411
(Tor Prakai) No. No.
(Nine) Nah.

543
00:31:20,411 --> 00:31:21,079
What should we do?

544
00:31:21,079 --> 00:31:22,080
They're scared.

545
00:31:22,797 --> 00:31:24,882
Look, they're trembling.

546
00:31:25,850 --> 00:31:26,684
They aren't surrender.

547
00:31:27,368 --> 00:31:28,169
If you're not surrender,

548
00:31:28,519 --> 00:31:30,722
we'll send you to your death!

549
00:31:31,322 --> 00:31:32,090
Be careful!

550
00:31:32,090 --> 00:31:32,890
Hey.

551
00:31:33,091 --> 00:31:33,891
Watch out.

552
00:31:34,926 --> 00:31:35,727
Hey.

553
00:31:38,329 --> 00:31:39,130
Be careful!

554
00:31:41,282 --> 00:31:42,284
Be careful!

555
00:31:42,593 --> 00:31:43,384
Ugh.

556
00:31:44,408 --> 00:31:45,295
Hey.

557
00:31:47,768 --> 00:31:48,704
Move, Pra Nine!

558
00:31:49,153 --> 00:31:50,000
Ugh!

559
00:31:51,232 --> 00:31:52,071
Come on!

560
00:31:52,427 --> 00:31:53,314
Ouch.

561
00:31:53,873 --> 00:31:55,583
Follow them!

562
00:32:02,854 --> 00:32:04,205
Why are you acting cool?

563
00:32:05,588 --> 00:32:06,427
Go! Go!

564
00:32:15,851 --> 00:32:16,835
Hey!

565
00:32:16,836 --> 00:32:17,904
Gosh!

566
00:32:19,017 --> 00:32:19,912
How wicked.

567
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:22,348
Will you surrender?

568
00:32:23,170 --> 00:32:24,310
If not,

569
00:32:24,504 --> 00:32:25,771
I'll send you

570
00:32:25,771 --> 00:32:27,241
to your death.

571
00:32:27,241 --> 00:32:28,083
I'll kill you!

572
00:32:28,084 --> 00:32:28,729
No!

573
00:32:28,729 --> 00:32:29,568
Stop it!

574
00:32:31,802 --> 00:32:32,593
Brother,

575
00:32:32,594 --> 00:32:34,013
please help me.

576
00:32:34,554 --> 00:32:35,732
They are thieves.

577
00:32:36,175 --> 00:32:37,981
They're trying to kill me and Pra Nine.

578
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:39,661
Don't worry. I'll save you.

579
00:32:39,661 --> 00:32:40,403
Hey!

580
00:32:45,337 --> 00:32:46,128
Anything funny?

581
00:32:46,488 --> 00:32:47,520
The jokers.

582
00:32:50,401 --> 00:32:51,769
Three of them.

583
00:32:53,805 --> 00:32:55,606
Do they know they're jokers?

584
00:32:56,841 --> 00:32:57,642
Do they know it?

585
00:32:58,009 --> 00:32:59,444
No. They are more good-looking than funny.

586
00:32:59,927 --> 00:33:00,728
Hey!

587
00:33:00,762 --> 00:33:01,393
