wherever stage you are,

876
00:49:53,640 --> 00:49:54,975
sparks of Likay

877
00:49:56,526 --> 00:49:57,844
will always be with you.

878
00:49:59,963 --> 00:50:01,815
Thanks a lot, P'Ploy.

879
00:50:05,602 --> 00:50:06,653
Anybody hungry?

880
00:50:06,653 --> 00:50:07,781
Me!

881
00:50:07,781 --> 00:50:08,959
Me too!

882
00:50:08,959 --> 00:50:10,000
Let's have something at our home.

883
00:50:11,742 --> 00:50:12,757
I'm hungry.

884
00:50:12,757 --> 00:50:13,787
Can you make me something, Ploy?

885
00:50:13,787 --> 00:50:14,335
Yeah.

886
00:50:14,335 --> 00:50:14,835
What?

887
00:50:14,835 --> 00:50:16,524
Can you make something for us, please?

888
00:50:16,524 --> 00:50:17,646
I can't. I'm tired.

889
00:50:22,519 --> 00:50:23,320
Okay.

890
00:50:24,481 --> 00:50:25,572
Let's go back to our home.

891
00:50:26,201 --> 00:50:29,680
Because the real leader is so starving.

892
00:50:31,373 --> 00:50:33,460
Whatever. I'll just wait and eat.

893
00:50:33,460 --> 00:50:35,078
Me too.

894
00:50:35,078 --> 00:50:36,304
I won't do the dishes.

895
00:50:36,304 --> 00:50:36,949
I'll do nothing.

896
00:50:36,949 --> 00:50:38,368
Leader should do it.

897
00:50:38,368 --> 00:50:39,712
P'Ploy, you should do it.
